# 3D Model Assets

Place GLTF/GLB model files here.

## Recommended Free Sources (CC0/Public Domain):
- Quaternius: https://quaternius.com/
- Poly Pizza: https://poly.pizza/
- Kenney Assets: https://kenney.nl/assets
- Sketchfab (filter by CC0): https://sketchfab.com/

## Suggested Models:
- turbine.glb - Main industrial rig/turbine model
- generator.glb - Power generator
- pipes.glb - Industrial piping

## Optimization:
- Use Draco compression for smaller file sizes
- Target <10K triangles per model for performance
- Export from Blender as GLTF 2.0 with Draco
